Package ru.rsreu.kuznecovsokolov12.datalayer

Interface UserDAO

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    OracleUserDAO
    public interface UserDAO
    The UserDAO interface provides methods for working with tables storing user data.

    This interface includes methods for retrieving users by ID or login, getting the expert for a team, retrieving a list of all users, getting a list of unprivileged users, retrieving a list of blocked users more than N times, getting the user list for a specific team, retrieving a map of users with their roles, getting the team captain for a team, adding a new user, updating user information, deleting a user, and getting a set of blocked users.
